item.title: CVE-2017-3264|2024-10-09T19:38:19.245Z -- oracle -- siebel%20ui%20framework
item.description: Vulnerability in the Siebel UI Framework component of Oracle Siebel CRM (subcomponent: Open UI). The supported version that is affected is 16.1. Difficult to exploit vulnerability allows low privileged attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Siebel UI Framework. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized update, insert or delete access to some of Siebel UI Framework accessible data. CVSS v3.0 Base Score 3.1 (Integrity impacts).
